cs.RO, cs.CV, cs.HC, cs.LG, cs.AI 

Reasoning: 
- cs.RO (Robotics) is the most likely category as the paper addresses the use of artificial neural networks for controlling an industrial robot through hand gestures. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is also likely as the paper deals with recognizing hand gestures using a data glove as interface technology. 
- cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction) is another possible category as the paper focuses on developing a more natural human-robot interface. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is a likely category as the paper uses artificial neural networks for gesture recognition. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also a possible category as the paper deals with developing an intelligent system for recognizing hand gestures in real-time.
